maya memsaab ( hindi : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) , also known as maya and maya : the enchanting illusion in english ) is a 1993 indian hindi film directed by ketan mehta . the film is based on gustave flaubert 's novel madame bovary . maya memsaab won the national film award - special jury award / special mention ( feature film ) in the year 1993 . the rights of this film are now owned by shah rukh khan 's red chillies entertainment .